909JSC_DEFINE_CUSTOM_GETTER(jsMathMLElementConstructor, (JSGlobalObject* lexicalGlobalObject, EncodedJSValue thisValue, PropertyName))
910{
911 VM& vm = JSC::getVM(lexicalGlobalObject);
912 auto throwScope = DECLARE_THROW_SCOPE(vm);
913 auto* prototype = jsDynamicCast<JSMathMLElementPrototype*>(vm, JSValue::decode(thisValue));
914 if (UNLIKELY(!prototype))
915 return throwVMTypeError(lexicalGlobalObject, throwScope);
916 return JSValue::encode(JSMathMLElement::getConstructor(JSC::getVM(lexicalGlobalObject), prototype->globalObject()));
917}

925}

931
932static inline bool setJSMathMLElement_styleSetter(JSGlobalObject& lexicalGlobalObject, JSMathMLElement& thisObject, JSValue value)
933{
934 auto& vm = JSC::getVM(&lexicalGlobalObject);
935 auto throwScope = DECLARE_THROW_SCOPE(vm);
936 auto id = Identifier::fromString(vm, reinterpret_cast<const LChar*>("style"), strlen("style"));
937 auto valueToForwardTo = thisObject.get(&lexicalGlobalObject, id);
938 RETURN_IF_EXCEPTION(throwScope, false);
939 if (UNLIKELY(!valueToForwardTo.isObject())) {
940 throwTypeError(&lexicalGlobalObject, throwScope);
941 return false;
942 }
943 auto forwardId = Identifier::fromString(vm, reinterpret_cast<const LChar*>("cssText"), strlen("cssText"));
944 PutPropertySlot slot(valueToForwardTo, false);
945 asObject(valueToForwardTo)->methodTable(vm)->put(asObject(valueToForwardTo), &lexicalGlobalObject, forwardId, value, slot);
946 RETURN_IF_EXCEPTION(throwScope, false);
947 return true;
948}

951{
952 return IDLAttribute<JSMathMLElement>::set<setJSMathMLElement_styleSetter>(*lexicalGlobalObject, thisValue, encodedValue, attributeName);
953}

965 thisObject.m_attributeStyleMap.set(JSC::getVM(&lexicalGlobalObject), &thisObject, result);
966 return result;
967}

3685 RELEASE_AND_RETURN(throwScope, JSValue::encode(toJS<IDLUndefined>(*lexicalGlobalObject, throwScope, [&]() -> decltype(auto) { return impl.focus(WTFMove(options)); })));
3686}

3708JSC::IsoSubspace* JSMathMLElement::subspaceForImpl(JSC::VM& vm)
3709{
3710 auto& clientData = *static_cast<JSVMClientData*>(vm.clientData);
3711 auto& spaces = clientData.subspaces();
3712 if (auto* space = spaces.m_subspaceForMathMLElement.get())
3713 return space;
3714 static_assert(std::is_base_of_v<JSC::JSDestructibleObject, JSMathMLElement> || !JSMathMLElement::needsDestruction);
3715 if constexpr (std::is_base_of_v<JSC::JSDestructibleObject, JSMathMLElement>)
3716 spaces.m_subspaceForMathMLElement = makeUnique<IsoSubspace> ISO_SUBSPACE_INIT(vm.heap, vm.destructibleObjectHeapCellType.get(), JSMathMLElement);
3717 else
3718 spaces.m_subspaceForMathMLElement = makeUnique<IsoSubspace> ISO_SUBSPACE_INIT(vm.heap, vm.cellHeapCellType.get(), JSMathMLElement);
3719 auto* space = spaces.m_subspaceForMathMLElement.get();
3720IGNORE_WARNINGS_BEGIN("unreachable-code")
3721IGNORE_WARNINGS_BEGIN("tautological-compare")
3722 void (*myVisitOutputConstraint)(JSC::JSCell*, JSC::SlotVisitor&) = JSMathMLElement::visitOutputConstraints;
3723 void (*jsCellVisitOutputConstraint)(JSC::JSCell*, JSC::SlotVisitor&) = JSC::JSCell::visitOutputConstraints;
3724 if (myVisitOutputConstraint != jsCellVisitOutputConstraint)
3725 clientData.outputConstraintSpaces().append(space);
3726IGNORE_WARNINGS_END
3727IGNORE_WARNINGS_END
3728 return space;
3729}
